---
title: Tunisian Pork & Veggie Couscous with Garlic Dip & Pumpkin Seeds
description: There's couscous and then there's veggie couscous. The key here is to cook it to fluffy perfection, then take it to another level by bringing
it together with the fresh and punchy elements of capsicum and spinach. It serves as the perfect bed for the juicy, spiced pork.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

